This tool is used to backup the database or file-system on client machine.
To use this tool, we need to install the dependency described in requirements.txt,
Please follow the below command:
1.   pip install -r requirements.txt

To deploy this project, we need to use cron to set the daily task schedule,
2. Use crontab -e to fill in above content.
-------------------------------------------------
|0 1 * * * python $PROJECT_DIR/backup-agent.py   |
-------------------------------------------------
The $PROJECT_DIR is the tool location.

3. Finally, fill in the backup.conf for any database or file-system you want to backup.

4. Test whether the module can run normally manually
--------------------------------------
| python $PROJECT_DIR/backup-agent.py |
--------------------------------------

Any problem, please contact Mei Lei <meil@rc.inesa.com>
